588
00:31:33,380 --> 00:31:34,400
No matter what,

589
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:37,960
Qiao Zishan's disappearance
must have something to do with him.

590
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:38,760
Let's do this—

591
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,070
