716
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:35,290
Nice to meet you.

717
00:39:35,370 --> 00:39:38,670
[Adult Psychiatric Clinic]

718
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:36,890
My name is Luo Liang.

719
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:38,360
Hello, Dr. Luo.

720
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:41,920
I'm Qiao Zishan.

721
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:44,190
Hello. Nice to meet you.

722
00:39:44,190 --> 00:39:45,030
Nice to meet you.

723
00:39:45,030 --> 00:39:47,230
How long have you been on Harbor Island?

724
00:39:57,400 --> 00:39:58,590
You must've been waiting a long time.

725
00:39:58,590 --> 00:39:59,070
No.

726
00:39:59,070 --> 00:39:59,550
No?

727
00:40:00,110 --> 00:40:00,970
This is for you.

728
00:40:01,230 --> 00:40:01,880
What is it?

729
00:40:06,110 --> 00:40:07,400
Sugar-Oil Fritters.

730
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:09,030
I heard you talking about them every day,

731
00:40:09,030 --> 00:40:11,150
saying you wanted to go back to Tanhua
to have some.

732
00:40:11,150 --> 00:40:12,710
When I went back to Shenchuan,
I searched everywhere

733
00:40:12,710 --> 00:40:14,840
and finally found a shop selling them.

734
00:40:48,510 --> 00:40:49,570
I can't use iodine.

735
00:40:51,030 --> 00:40:53,290
The color of iodine will ruin the tattoo.

736
00:40:53,550 --> 00:40:54,800
It's just a tattoo.

737
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:57,810
Does it really hurt that much?

738
00:40:59,720 --> 00:41:01,320
No one else reacted like you.

739
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:02,840
Sorry.

740
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:06,620
While I was showering,

741
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:08,480
my mom noticed it.

742
00:41:09,840 --> 00:41:13,100
I was trying to hide it from her
and accidentally got it wet.

743
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:18,680
You're no longer your mom's
good little girl—

744
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:21,120
that must have made her very sad, right?

745
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:22,440
I...

746
00:41:23,190 --> 00:41:23,800
told her

747
00:41:25,030 --> 00:41:26,900
I wanted the tattoo myself.

748
00:41:31,150 --> 00:41:32,550
So you didn't tell her...

749
00:41:33,230 --> 00:41:34,690
this is a token of our love,

750
00:41:35,110 --> 00:41:36,370
proof that you love me?

751
00:41:39,230 --> 00:41:41,850
I just didn't want to make her mad.

752
00:41:42,670 --> 00:41:44,250
I'm with you...

753
00:41:44,630 --> 00:41:46,830
She doesn't want you to be with me at all!

754
00:41:47,150 --> 00:41:49,070
She wants you to go abroad to marry up.

755
00:41:49,070 --> 00:41:51,200
She wants you to marry a rich foreigner

756
00:41:51,360 --> 00:41:52,510
and bring her over.

757
00:41:54,480 --> 00:41:55,410
That's not true.

758
00:41:56,280 --> 00:41:57,710
My mom isn't like that.

759
00:41:59,110 --> 00:42:00,840
Then why did she marry an old man

760
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:02,380
and come to Harbor Island?

761
00:42:03,240 --> 00:42:05,150
Wasn't she chasing a better life?

762
00:42:06,760 --> 00:42:07,800
Now that she's old

763
00:42:08,550 --> 00:42:10,610
and can't trade on her looks anymore,

764
00:42:11,030 --> 00:42:12,290
she's counting on you.

765
00:42:13,130 --> 00:42:14,860
She wants you to sell yourself.

766
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:18,000
To her, right now,

767
00:42:18,970 --> 00:42:19,710
I'm just

768
00:42:19,710 --> 00:42:23,640
a poor student preventing you from
marrying rich and rising to the top.

769
00:42:29,230 --> 00:42:30,560
Maybe your mom is right.

770
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,800
You shouldn't have been with me.

771
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:39,800
No.

772
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:42,080
It's not like that.

773
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:45,200
I'm not that kind of person.

774
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:47,640
I would never do that.

775
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:49,040
Please believe me.

776
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:51,800
I swear,

777
00:42:52,630 --> 00:42:54,720
I will never leave you!

778
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:05,710
I believe you.

779
00:43:09,840 --> 00:43:11,660
I've never doubted you.

780
00:43:16,030 --> 00:43:17,040
The two of us...

781
00:43:18,400 --> 00:43:20,400
are like reflections of each other.

782
00:43:21,800 --> 00:43:24,030
We both came from terrible backgrounds,

783
00:43:24,030 --> 00:43:26,030
with the worst fathers imaginable.

784
00:43:28,440 --> 00:43:29,700
Our meeting

785
00:43:30,400 --> 00:43:31,960
was fated.

786
00:43:33,880 --> 00:43:34,630
We...

787
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:40,640
are the greatest gift
heaven could have given each other.

788
00:43:42,400 --> 00:43:42,920
Yes.

789
00:43:44,960 --> 00:43:45,590
Yes.

790
00:43:48,180 --> 00:43:49,850
We are one.

791
00:43:52,510 --> 00:43:54,550
No one can separate us.

792
00:43:56,340 --> 00:43:58,530
No one can separate us.

